---
import Main from "../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Main title="Copyright | Confessions Hub">
  <section class="copyright card-panel">
    <h1>Copyright Info</h1>
    <h2>Matthew 10:8 "...Freely you have received; freely give."</h2>
    <p>
      Unless otherwise stated all of our website and its content is within the Public Domain and can be
      used by anyone without restriction. No attribution is necessary but it is a kind thing to do.
      Feel free to translate or copy or share.
    </p>
    <p>
      Everything we have provided in Confessions Hub is already public domain source material.
    </p>
    <p>
      To avoid confusion, we ask that you do not use the Confessions Hub branding or logo for
      adaptations not associated with us (unless such use is covered under fair-use laws).
    </p>
    <h2>Licensing</h2>
    <p>
      If you believe any content attribution or source labeling is incorrect or needs to be updated, please use the
      <a href="https://github.com/abereanone/confession/issues/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        issue form
      </a>
      and include the exact page and text in question.
    </p>
  </section>
</Main>

<style>
  .copyright {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .copyright p {
    margin: 0.65rem 0;
  }
</style>
